snippet.title: Starfighter 3000 gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Starfighter 3000, Dos PC game produced by Acclaim in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/starfighter-3000/8217/
Playing through the first mission after watching the lenghty introduction. Trying to spot the target and finally crashing on the hill due to reduced visibility.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
